This 7 acre property features pasture areas, a tack shed with a deck to observe the rider(s), a garden area, plum and apple trees, raspberries, various herbs and more! Fresh outside paint, brand new epoxy floor in the heated garage with a pet washing station, updated kitchen and laminate flooring throughout with carpet in the primary suite.
